50 «Живая мишень»), Ковалёв\n2010 — «Маршрут милосердия»\n2010 — «1942», эпизод\n2008 — «Безумный ноябрь», номинант\n2007 — «Возвращение Мухтара-4», (серия 28 «Практическая магия»), Санин\n2006 — «Девять жизней Нестора Махно», эпизод\nНаграды\nЗаслуженный артист Украины (23.03.1998).\nНародный артист Украины (07.11.2014).','Victor Aldoshin (b. August 8, 1960) — Ukrainian theater and cinema actor, actor of the National academic theater of Russian drama named after Lesya Ukrainka (Kiev). People\'s artist of Ukraine (2014).\n\nBiography\nBorn August 8, 1960.\n\nIn 1984 he graduated from Kyiv Institute of theatrical art named after Karpenko-Kary.\n\nIn the years 1984-1999 — actor Kirovohrad regional Ukrainian musical-drama theatre named after M. kropyvnytskyi.\n\n1999 — actor of the National academic theater of Russian drama named after Lesya Ukrainka (Kiev).\n\nCreativity\nTheater roles\nThe performances of the current repertoire of the National academic theater of Russian drama named after Lesya Ukrainka\n\n\"Everywhere one...\"(Taras Shevchenko)\n\"The cherry orchard\" (Simeonov-Pishchik, Boris Borisovich, the landlord)\n\"Trees die standing\" (the Pastor)\n\"A real man at the beginning of the Millennium...» (Father)\n\"Freeloader\" (Ivan Kuzmitch Ivanov, another neighbor; Vassily Semyonitch Kuzovkin, a gentleman, living on bread at Yelets)\n\"Too happy, father\" (Daddy)\n\"A liar!\"(Theofilos Perakis, MP)\n\"School for scandal\" (Carless)\nTheatrical work\n\n\"Just flickers a ghostly scene... (Anniversary. Anniversary? Anniversary!)\" (2011)\n\"Don Quixote 1938\" (2006)\n\"All Shakespeare for one evening\" (2005)\n\"Masquerade\" (2004)\n\"Wolves and sheep\" (2003)\n\"New year surprises\" (2003)\n\"Lulu. The History Of Courtesans\" (2002)\n\"And it was... And all of this will\" (2002)\n\"Vengeance Italian\" (2000)\n\"Flea in the ear\" (1998)\nFilmography\n2014 — \"so far, So close\", Grigory Tikhonovich, father-in-law Nasti\n2012 — \"Five years and a day\" episode\n2